Jenson Button Wins Rain-Hit Canadian Grand Prix, Sebastian Vettel Second

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-06-12T21:09:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/jenson-button-wins-rain-hit-canadian-grand-prix-sebastian-vettel-second.html
Jenson Button of McLaren won today’s
rain-hit Canadian Grand Prix as Red Bull’s Sebastian Vettel blew
the race with a last-lap error.  Series leader Vettel was second at the Circuit Gilles-
Villeneuve in  Montreal . His teammate  Mark Webber  was third.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  